{"tid":2102683,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解黃店頌係免費派防疫物資比人？","createTime":"2020-07-10T15:52:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-10T16:18:32.000Z","uid":252031,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"79366ccff5381750517b4d867c8d2a40c4dad532","tid":2102683,"uid":252031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T15:52:44.000Z","msg":"香港咁細，咁多單源頭不明嘅個案<br />\n爆就爆硬㗎啦<br />\n其實只要自己做好防疫措施<br />\n戴口罩 勤洗手 飲多d水<br />\n基本上都已經夠安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n啲藍屍唔做足<br />\n要爆未由佢囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n爆咗可以繼續封關<br />\n政府繼續派錢<br />\n我地一路拎錢一路反政府<br />\n要派物質未派比自己食客<br />\n點解頌要無差別咁任人拎？<br />\n<br />\n由第一日開始我已經唔明<br />\n賺黃絲嘅錢去倒貼藍屍<br />\n入不敷支嘅時候又告急<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要派唔該都起碼係派比客人<br />\n有消費又證明係同路人<br />\n點解要益啲貪心藍屍廢老？"},{"pid":"9c8cd43a1ecf8a4a027d6311fd191bc7833addff","tid":2102683,"uid":270237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T15:54:17.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">港共越係唔想我投<br />\n我越係要去投</span></strong></span><br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"orange\">港共越係唔想我投<br />\n我越係要去投</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">港共越係唔想我投<br />\n我越係要去投</span></span></strong><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"limegreen\">港共越係唔想我投<br />\n我越係要去投</span></strong></span><br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"green\">港共越係唔想我投<br />\n我越係要去投</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"blue\">港共越係唔想我投<br />\n我越係要去投</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"purple\">港共越係唔想我投<br />\n我越係要去投</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"949369da9b2e39e7f42467ef6314c362c5a1c00f","tid":2102683,"uid":252031,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T15:54:33.000Z","msg":"警告各大黃店，唔好又搞乜柒醫護優惠<br /